{# Joint-organisers strip (Issue #198).

   Renders a polished horizontal grid of co-organising institutions
   for joint events. Each org becomes a stacked sponsor card — fixed-
   size white logo slot above the institution name. The whole card is
   the link when a URL is provided. Equal-width grid columns ensure
   the three native logo aspect ratios (EISS lockup, NetSec mark +
   wordmark, Stockholm University landscape wordmark) read with
   equivalent visual weight regardless of native dimensions.

   Required argument:
     jointOrgs — array of { name, url?, logo? } objects.
                   name  required, plain text
                   url   optional, omit to render the card as a non-
                         interactive block instead of a link
                   logo  optional, path under /assets/images/. When
                         set, renders the logo above the name. When
                         unset, the name carries on its own.

   Optional argument:
     jointOrgsLabel — short heading shown centred above the grid.
                      Defaults to "Jointly organised with" but can
                      be overridden, e.g. "Hosts", "In partnership
                      with", or the locale equivalent.

   Example call from a conference page:

     {%- set jointOrgs = [
       { name: "Stockholm University", url: "https://www.su.se/",
         logo: "/assets/images/partners/stockholm-uni.svg" },
       { name: "NetSec (COST Action CA24154)",
         url: "https://netsec-cost.eu/" }
     ] -%}
     {% include "joint-orgs.njk" %}

   No-op when `jointOrgs` is empty or undefined, so it's safe to
   include conditionally without guarding at each call site. -#}
{%- if jointOrgs and (jointOrgs | length) > 0 -%}
{%- set _label = jointOrgsLabel or 'Jointly organised with' -%}
<div class="joint-orgs" role="complementary" aria-label="{{ _label }}">
  <p class="joint-orgs-label">{{ _label }}</p>
  <ul class="joint-orgs-list">
    {%- for org in jointOrgs %}
    <li class="joint-orgs-item">
      {%- if org.url -%}
      <a class="joint-orgs-card" href="{{ org.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      {%- else -%}
      <div class="joint-orgs-card">
      {%- endif %}
        {%- if org.logo %}
        <span class="joint-orgs-logo-slot">
          <img class="joint-orgs-logo"
               src="{{ org.logo }}"
               alt=""
               loading="lazy">
        </span>
        {%- endif %}
        <span class="joint-orgs-name">{{ org.name }}</span>
      {%- if org.url -%}
      </a>
      {%- else -%}
      </div>
      {%- endif %}
    </li>
    {%- endfor %}
  </ul>
</div>
{%- endif -%}
